content.text: Located 2.7 mi (4.3 km) from the airport, New York Marriott Marquis offers a great location, putting you within just a 10-minute walk of Broadway and Times Square. Guests can visit the 24-hour fitness center for a workout or grab a bite to eat at The View Restaurant, one of 2 restaurants, which serves American cuisine and is open for dinner. Other highlights at this luxurious hotel include a bar/lounge and a snack bar/deli. Fellow travelers like the central location for the sightseeing and because it's just a short walk to public transportation: 49th St. Station is steps away and Times Sq. - 42 St. Station is 5 minutes.
